I only found out the set times the day before with Doechii listed for Saturday so I decided the next day to head down ticketless. Found one for $50 just outside the gates. Unfortunately missed Noah Cyrus and the first 2 songs of Sophie Ellis-Bextor where I was recording with only the internal microphones as I was getting the lay of the land and figuring out where I wanted to set up for the rest of the evening. I wanted to go back the next day for Kylie Minogue but just couldn't get moving. Doechii was great, actually seen her 3 times this month so far. I did get most of Pride In The Park headlined by Ricky Martin the next week but not much chance to check it out yet.
